974
0:47:26,803 --> 0:47:31,128
watch out, middle class. The tax bill is coming to you.


975
0:47:31,128 --> 0:47:34,264
That's why we're saying we need fundamental tax reform.


976
0:47:34,264 --> 0:47:35,733
Let's take a look at it this way:


977
0:47:35,733 --> 0:47:39,31
8-out-of-10 businesses, they file their taxes as individuals,


978
0:47:39,31 --> 0:47:40,226
not as corporations.


979
0:47:40,226 --> 0:47:42,302
