1653
1:15:50,319 --> 1:15:55,645
with the exceptions for rape, incest and life of the mother.


1654
1:15:55,645 --> 1:15:59,823
What troubles me more is how this administration has handled


1655
1:15:59,823 --> 1:16:1,54
all of these issues.


1656
1:16:1,54 --> 1:16:4,368
Look at what they're doing through "Obamacare"


1657
1:16:4,368 --> 1:16:8,308
with respect to assaulting the religious liberties of this country.


1658
1:16:8,308 --> 1:16:13,861
