1659
1:16:13,861 --> 1:16:15,936
by infringing on Catholic charities,


1660
1:16:15,936 --> 1:16:19,58
Catholic churches, Catholic hospitals.


1661
1:16:19,58 --> 1:16:21,273
Our church should not have to sue our federal government


1662
1:16:21,273 --> 1:16:22,929
to maintain their religious — religious liberties.


1663
1:16:22,929 --> 1:16:25,401
And with respect to abortion,


1664
1:16:25,401 --> 1:16:29,12
the Democratic Party used to say they want it to be safe, legal and rare.


1665
1:16:29,12 --> 1:16:33,314
